detail.name: Bardock
detail.effect:
[Critical] (When this card inflicts damage with an attack, the life is placed in the Drop.)
[Auto][Your Turn][Once per turn] If your Leader is <Bardock>, when your card is used in a combo while this card is in a battle, choose up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 4 or less in your opponent's Battle Area and KO it.
